  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are able to output a massive amount of force inherent to you due to your Twisted Chakra. This power acts like a steroid with seemingly no drawback. This strength feels bottomless.</p><p>You gain the following benefits while you are under the effects of Desperate Rage or Twisted Chakra Cloak:</p><p>• Taijutsu and Bukijutsu you cast apply your Proficiency bonus to damage rolls.<br />• Attacks, Jutsu, or Features that use your Strength and Vermilion Arts ignore Damage Reduction and Resistance and treat Immunity as Resistance.<br />• Taijutsu and Bukijutsu you are concentrating on cannot be ended by damage, being Incapacitated, or losing the ability to mold chakra.</p>",
